entered-japanese-waters-japans-defence-ministry-says-2024-08-31/</guid></item><item><title>中国、菲律宾互相指责对方在南海撞船</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-coast-guard-says-philippine-ship-rammed-chinese-vessel-south-china-sea-2024-08-31/</link><description>周六，菲律宾和中国相互指责在南海有争议的水域故意撞击海岸警卫队船只，这是这条重要水道上一系列不断升级的冲突中的最新一起。</description><pubDate>Sat, 31 Aug 2024 08:09:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-coast-guard-says-philippine-ship-rammed-chinese-vessel-south-china-sea-2024-08-31/</guid></item><item><title>联合国关于中国侵权行为的报告两年后，挫败感加深</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/frustration-deepens-two-years-after-un-report-china-abuses-2024-08-31/</link><description>中国坚决否认新疆存在任何侵权行为。</description><pubDate>Sat, 31 Aug 2024 06:06:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/frustration-deepens-two-years-after-un-report-china-abuses-2024-08-31/</guid></item><item><title>中国疲软的工厂PMI增加了刺激消费的压力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-august-manufacturing-activity-falls-fourth-month-2024-08-31/</link><description>周六的一项官方调查显示，由于工厂出厂价格暴跌，业主难以获得订单，中国八月份的制造业活动跌至六个月低点，迫使政策制定者继续实施针对家庭的更多刺激计划。</description><pubDate>Sat, 31 Aug 2024 01:39:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-august-manufacturing-activity-falls-fourth-month-2024-08-31/</guid></item><item><title>在中国提出抗议后，太平洋领导人将台湾从公报中删除</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/pacific-leaders-remove-taiwan-communique-after-china-complaint-2024-08-31/</link><description>该论坛成员中，3 个与台湾有外交关系，15 个承认中国。</description><pubDate>Sat, 31 Aug 2024 01:32:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/pacific-leaders-remove-taiwan-communique-after-china-complaint-2024-08-31/</guid></item><item><title>美国称RTX因向中国和其他国家出口而被罚款2亿美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/rtx-pay-200-million-fine-export-mistakes-state-department-says-2024-08-30/</link><description>美国国务院周四的记录称，RTX Corp 将支付 2 亿美元罚款，以了结有关这家航空航天和国防公司因与包括中国在内的被禁止国家交换数据和产品而违反出口法的指控。</description><pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 13:57:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/rtx-pay-200-million-fine-export-mistakes-state-department-says-2024-08-30/</guid></item><item><title>由于房地产行业承压，中国顶级银行第二季度利润下降</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-top-banks-post-lower-second-quarter-profit-property-sector-weighs-2024-08-30/</link><description>中国五家最大的银行中有四家本周报告第二季度利润下降，此前政府为在经济放缓和房地产行业陷入困境的情况下刺激贷款需求而降低贷款利率。</description><pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 13:48:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-top-banks-post-lower-second-quarter-profit-property-sector-weighs-2024-08-30/</guid></item><item><title>美国贸易代表办公室推迟对中国关税的最终决定，未来几天将发布公告</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/ustr-says-decision-section-301-tariffs-chinese-imports-be-announced-coming-days-2024-08-30/</link><description>拜登政府周五再次推迟宣布美国对中国制造的电动汽车、电池、半导体和太阳能电池大幅提高关税的最终决定，并表示将在未来几天内公布决定。</description><pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 13:26:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/ustr-says-decision-section-301-tariffs-chinese-imports-be-announced-coming-days-2024-08-30/</guid></item><item><title>西班牙首相桑切斯下月访华，因中欧贸易争端</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/spains-sanchez-visit-china-next-month-amid-beijing-eu-trade-dispute-2024-08-30/</link><description>西班牙首相佩德罗·桑切斯办公室周五表示，以北京对欧盟猪肉进口反倾销调查为背景，西班牙首相佩德罗·桑切斯将于下个月访问中国。</description><pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 12:57:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/spains-sanchez-visit-china-next-month-amid-beijing-eu-trade-dispute-2024-08-30/</guid></item><item><title>国务院审议通过数据安全管理条例草案</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-cabinet-passes-draft-regulations-data-security-management-2024-08-30/</link><description>官方媒体周五称，中国国务院已通过数据安全管理条例草案。</description><pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 11:28:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-cabinet-passes-draft-regulations-data-security-management-2024-08-30/</guid></item><item><title>中国市场监管机构称电子商务巨头阿里巴巴已完成三年“整顿”期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/chinas-market-regulator-says-e-commerce-giant-alibaba-has-completed-three-year-2024-08-30/</link><description>中国国家市场监管总局周五发表声明称，阿里巴巴集团继2021年因垄断行为被处以罚款后，已完成三年“整改”。</description><pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 09:59:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/chinas-market-regulator-says-e-commerce-giant-alibaba-has-completed-three-year-2024-08-30/</guid></item><item><title>台军方称中国缺乏入侵能力，但还有其他选择</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-ministry-says-china-lacks-ability-invade-has-other-options-2024-08-30/</link><description>台湾国防部表示，中国缺乏“全面”入侵台湾的能力，因为它没有装备，但正在引进先进的新武器，并有其他选择来威胁台湾，例如检查外国货船。</description><pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 08:13:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-ministry-says-china-lacks-ability-invade-has-other-options-2024-08-30/</guid></item></channel></rss>